{{define "subject"}}Your project awaits. Start collaborating today{{ end }}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi, 
You`ve been invited by {{.inviterName}} to join the project "{{.projectName}}".
To accept the invitation, log in to the platform: https://bipc.com.br/login
This invitation will expire in 7 days.
Thanks,
The BIPC Team
{{ end }}

{{define "htmlBody"}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  </head>
