      To accept the invitation, log in to the platform: <a href="http://bipc.com.br/login">log in here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>This invitation will expire in 7 days.</p>
    <p>
      Thanks,<br />
      The BIPC Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
{{ end }}
